column5: hey guys what rods do you reccomend for 100-300 lbs catfish? going on holidays to a country called Latvia, my relatives will show me a river "daugava" where people constantly catch 100+ lb catfish.
A better question may be, how many of you people have caught a 100 - 300 pound catfish? Just guessing at very low numbers?
This is a question for Jeremy Wade
Search for Wels Catfish Tackle. Eques Wels/GT/Tuna Stick
I’d guess you’d best order from Europe to find the right gear.
